  <div><em>Browser extension which gives you more control over YouTube by adding missing options and UI improvements - for desktop &amp; mobile browsers</em></div>
  <details><summary>v1.20.1 release notes</summary><h2>Changes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Always use original audio now also works for Shorts on desktop</li>
<li>Fixed some video hiding options not working in Related when using the new option to only hide Related when it appears below the video</li>
<li>Fixed Block ads conflicting with other adblockers when disabled</li>
<li>Added a note to the Block ads option that you should disable it if already using another adblocker</li>
</ul>
